and this device- this switch is the wired link.

00:07:00.020 --> 00:07:03.840
But communication can happen
through this intermediary devices.

00:07:04.260 --> 00:07:06.940
Similarly, if this
smart-phone also wants

00:07:06.940 --> 00:07:10.300
