from nesoacademy.org,

00:07:10.300 --> 00:07:13.000
this can also give the
request but this request

00:07:13.000 --> 00:07:15.680
can be carried out either
this way or this way.

00:07:15.680 --> 00:07:18.580
But if you observe both in the ways, they are wireless.

00:07:18.580 --> 00:07:22.100
So the same server can be
accessed with the help of wires

00:07:22.100 --> 00:07:23.960
as well as with the
help of wireless.

